title: Stevo - Multiverse (Goa Trance Mix)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

High-octane newschool Goa trance mix by DJ Stevo made for special Neogoa Records anniversary featuring some of the most exciting Goa trance production! Download full mix in best audio-quality here: http://www.neogoa.net/multiverse/

Tracklist:

01 - Trinodia - Deceive My Eyes
02 - Grand-Cheff - Lady Of Steel
03 - Agneton - Wizards From The Future (Afterlife Mix)
04 - Sky Technology - Lost Worlds
05 - Mindsphere - To Infinity (2010 Mix)
06 - Project Shidartha - Astral Levitation
07 - Radical Distortion - Goa Station
08 - Nova Fractal - Perplexed
09 - Cosmic Silence - Electric Manna
10 - BlackStarrFinale - Classic Attack
11 - Arronax & Somnesia - The Black Hole (Extended Trip)

More Neogoa Records at:

http://www.youtube.com/c/neogoarecords
